                      ReqHunter 1.1 (November 14, 2011)

This is version 1.1 of ReqHunter, a software for managing project requirements.

Installation Instructions
=========================
Simply execute the shell script ReqHunter.sh if you are using a GNU/Linux 
system, or the batch file ReqHunter.bat if you are not lucky and you have to
use MS-Windows.
